name: PalindromeGame
0:
”Alexa, Ask Palindrome game to give me five numbers”
”Alexa, Tell Palindrome game to give me seven”
”Alexa, Open Palindrome game and give me six”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: palindrome game
Developer Terms of Use
des: Alexa will give you a list of numbers. All you need to do is repeat them, but in reverse order! Most people can reverse four or five digits. Some can do six or seven. See how many you can do? No fair writing them down!
